WEBVTT

00:07:28.687 --> 00:07:31.367
Unahitaji kuwa na dharura kwa
yale yasiyoonekana,

00:07:31.391 --> 00:07:33.867
yasiyotegemewa na yasiyojulikana,

00:07:33.891 --> 00:07:36.544
muda yanapotokea na namna yanavyotokea.

00:07:38.150 --> 00:07:41.747
Sasa, kwa kutumia sanaa kuongeza
maarifa ya uono

00:07:41.771 --> 00:07:43.832
hujumuisha kupanga kwa dharura,

00:07:43.856 --> 00:07:46.254
kuelewa picha kubwa na taarifa ndogo

00:07:46.278 --> 00:07:47.913
na kugundua kipi kinachokosekana.

00:07:48.399 --> 00:07:50.853
Hivyo mchoro huu uliochorwa na Magritte,

00:07:50.877 --> 00:07:54.027
kugundua kwamba hakuna reli
chini ya treni,

00:07:54.051 --> 00:07:56.215
hakuna moto katika sehemu ya moto

00:07:56.239 --> 00:07:58.417
na hakuna mishumaa
ndani ya vinara

00:07:58.441 --> 00:08:01.258
kiuhalisia inaelezea mchoro